<template lang="pug">
  #Home
    GameCardsStack(:cards="cards",
                    @cardAccepted="handleCardAccepted",
                    @cardRejected="handleCardRejected",
                    @cardSkipped="handleCardSkipped",
                    @hideCard="removeCardFromDeck")
    v-layout.mt-12(justify-center)
      v-btn.mx-3(large, fab, :style="!buttonsDisabled ? 'border: 4px solid #F44336' : ''", :disabled="buttonsDisabled", @click="$root.$emit('rejectCard')")
        v-icon(color="tred") far fa-thumbs-down
      v-btn.mx-3(large, fab, :style="!buttonsDisabled ? 'border: 4px solid #2196F3' : ''", :disabled="buttonsDisabled", @click="buy")
        v-icon(color="tblue") fas fa-shopping-cart
      v-btn.mx-3(large, fab, :style="!buttonsDisabled ? 'border: 4px solid #FFC107' : ''", :disabled="buttonsDisabled")
        v-icon(color="tyellow") far fa-star
      v-btn.mx-3(large, fab, :style="!buttonsDisabled ? 'border: 4px solid #4CAF50' : ''", :disabled="buttonsDisabled", @click="$root.$emit('acceptCard')")
        v-icon(color="tgreen") far fa-thumbs-up
</template>

<script lang="ts">
import Vue from 'vue';
import GameCardsStack from '@/components/GameCardsStack.vue';

export default Vue.extend({
  components: {
    GameCardsStack,
  },

  computed: {
    cards: {
      get() {
        return this.$store.state.stack.cards;
      },
      set(value) {
        this.$store.commit('stack/setCards', value);
      },
    },

    buttonsDisabled() {
      return this.cards[0].type !== 'clothing';
    },
  },

  methods: {
    handleCardAccepted() {
      console.log('handleCardAccepted');
    },
    handleCardRejected() {
      console.log('handleCardRejected');
    },
    handleCardSkipped() {
      console.log('handleCardSkipped');
    },
    removeCardFromDeck() {
      this.$store.commit('stack/shift');
    },
    buy() {
      window.open(`https://www.amazon.es${this.cards[0].url}&linkCode=ll1&tag=mouo-21&linkId=c7cee5388cfffae3e66db9880a2dab3f&language=es_ES`);
    },
  },

});
</script>
